INSERT INTO `nsusa_posts` VALUES (2,1,'2013-09-09 20:00:51','2013-09-09 20:00:51','','Home','','publish','open','open','','sample-page','','','2015-04-13 09:14:51','2015-04-13 15:14:51','',0,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?page_id=2',9,'page','',0),(11,1,'2013-10-14 19:47:37','2013-10-14 19:47:37','','Home','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2013-10-14 19:47:37','2013-10-14 19:47:37','',2,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?p=11',0,'revision','',0),(12,1,'2013-10-14 19:48:55','2013-10-14 19:48:55','<i>Just for Fun </i>is not only our tagline but truly our approach to business. Our mission is to create product that allows our customers to get outside and enjoy all nature has to offer with friends and family. Whether it’s a day packed with building snowmen and tubing, or a night filled with campfire s’mores and ghost stories, Northside is literally there for you every step of the way.\r\n\r\nBased in Marysville, Wash., Northside by Triple T Trading is the recognized leader in recreational outdoor footwear. Offering a range of products from winter boots and trail shoes to sandals and flip-flops, Northside shoes are rugged, reliable and affordable for families who want to enjoy the outdoors together. Triple T Trading, the parent company for the Northside brand, was founded in 1985 with the goal to design, manufacture and sell well-made footwear at a great value.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;','Who We Are','','publish','open','open','','who-we-are','','','2013-12-06 19:04:36','2013-12-06 19:04:36','',0,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?page_id=12',8,'page','',0),(13,1,'2013-10-14 19:48:55','2013-10-14 19:48:55','','Our Story','','inherit','open','open','','12-revision-v1','','','2013-10-14 19:48:55','2013-10-14 19:48:55','',12,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?p=13',0,'revision','',0),(14,1,'2013-10-14 19:49:10','2013-10-14 19:49:10','[SLPLUS]','Find a Retailer','','publish','open','open','','find-a-retailer','','','2013-10-31 17:24:16','2013-10-31 17:24:16','',0,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?page_id=14',7,'page','',0),(15,1,'2013-10-14 19:49:10','2013-10-14 19:49:10','','Find a Retailer','','inherit','open','open','','14-revision-v1','','','2013-10-14 19:49:10','2013-10-14 19:49:10','',14,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?p=15',0,'revision','',0),(16,1,'2013-10-14 19:49:22','2013-10-14 19:49:22','<strong>Mailing address</strong>\r\nPO Box 124\r\nMarysville, WA 98271\r\n\r\n<strong>Phone Number</strong>\r\n<strong></strong><a href=\"tel:800-791-2582\" target=\"_blank\">800-791-2582</a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Email</strong>\r\n<a href=\"mailto:Contact@northsideusa.com\" target=\"_blank\">Contact@northsideusa.com</a>\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"15669\" title=\"Contact Us\"]','Contact','','publish','open','open','','contact','','','2013-11-20 13:52:38','2013-11-20 13:52:38','',0,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?page_id=16',6,'page','',0),(17,1,'2013-10-14 19:49:22','2013-10-14 19:49:22','','Contact','','inherit','open','open','','16-revision-v1','','','2013-10-14 19:49:22','2013-10-14 19:49:22','',16,'http://northsideusa.com/2014/?p=17',0,'revision','',0),(21352,1,'2012-08-01 10:35:56','1970-01-01 00:00:00','<strong>MARYSVILLE, Wash. (Aug 1, 2012) </strong>– <a href=\"http://www.northsideusa.com\" target=\"_blank\">Northside</a>, a leader in comfortable, durable and affordable outdoor and lifestyle footwear, will be introducing new styles for the whole family at <strong>Outdoor Retailer Summer Market 2012, Booth #29131</strong>. Northside’s new footwear designs are reliable and comfortable from the trail to the river, or for kicking around town all summer.\r\n\r\nThe Northside brand, now 12 years old, represents quality, rugged, reliable and affordable footwear available in contemporary styles for all members of the family. Northside’s lighthearted, down to earth branding stems from the company’s core values, one of which identifies the importance of lasting experiences that result from families enjoying the outdoors together.\r\n\r\n“We couldn’t be happier with our new line for Spring ’13,” said Jack Wolfin, president of Triple T Trading. “Our designers have really taken the sport and water shoe categories to the next level with quality footwear designs that bring style and comfort to families at a reasonable price.”\r\n\r\n<strong>NEW for Spring/Summer 2013:</strong>\r\n\r\n<em>TRAIL / LIFESTYLE:</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Northside Men’s Caldera – SRP $35</strong>\r\nThe Caldera was designed with suede and mesh upper making this day hiker rugged yet comfortable. An abrasion resistant PVC heel and toe guard and TPR traction outsole provide support and protection from trail debris. Sizes M 8 – 13. Available in Stone/Yellow.\r\n\r\n<strong>Northside Women’s Kiona LTC – SRP $50</strong>\r\nReady for the trail, the women’s Kiona LTC was developed with a combination of ultra-lightweight soft shell and breathable mesh to keep feet comfortable and dry on the go. The compression molded EVA midsole paired with the high traction outsole makes this sporty shoe perfect for road to trail. Sizes W 6 – 10. Available in Black/Purple and Grey/Fuchsia\r\n\r\n<strong>Northside Kids Cheyenne / Cheyenne Jr. – SRP $25</strong>\r\nThese durable little hikers offer a nice lightweight fit and feel. The suede and mesh upper provides breathability while the high traction outsole gives sure footing for exploring the outdoors. Cushioned for a comfortable fit with a quick lacing system (or Velcro) for the perfect fit. Sizes: Toddler 5 – 10, Boys 4-7, Girls 11-5, Kids 11-3. Available in Tan/Aqua and Taupe/Mango.\r\n\r\n<strong>Northside Del Rio LTC – SRP $40</strong>\r\nFeaturing an all-new urban casual design, the Del Rio LTC is styled for everyday wear with the outdoors in mind. A unique combination of breathable mesh materials, a fixed stretch neoprene tongue and a nylon Speed Lace System, the Del Rio LTC is designed to mold to your foot for long-term comfort. <strong>Available in men’s, women’s and children’s</strong> specific sizes and colors.\r\n\r\n<strong>Northside Women’s Del Sol LTC – SRP $40</strong>\r\nThe Women’s Del Sol is the perfect mix of urban style and everyday comfort. The breathable mesh sock construction and Speed Lacing System make the Del Sol a hip option for work and play.  Sizes W 6 – 10. Available in Grey/Pink, Brown/Purple and Grey/Green.\r\n\r\n<em>WATER:</em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Northside Raging River – SRP $50</strong>\r\nThis all-purpose water shoe features a contour cushioned perforated EVA insole and TPR traction outsole with drainage ports to allow easy water flow. The comfortable sock constructed upper and Drawstring Speed Lacing System allow for perfect fit. A quick-dry mesh upper ensures that feet won’t be left soggy. Sizes M 8 – 13, W 6 - 10. Available for men in Black/Green and Grey/Yellow, and for women in Grey/Light Blue and Grey/Fuchsia.\r\n\r\n<strong>Northside Burke II – SRP $25 - $30</strong>\r\nPossibly the most popular shoe in the Northside Sport Line, the Burke II is the refined version of it’s predecessor. Developed with a contour cushioned brushed EVA insole and TPR outsole for sure-step and foot protection. This amphibious shoe features waterproof PU and EVA lined upper for extra comfort and the Elastic Drawstring Lacing System and Lace Keeper. <strong>Available in men’s, women’s and children’s</strong> specific sizes and colors.\r\n\r\nNorthside shoes are available at more than 500 retailers and major online stores nationwide. Northside shoes typically retail from $29 to $69.\r\n\r\n<strong>About Verde PR &amp; Consulting</strong>\r\nWith offices in Durango and Boulder, Colo. and Jackson, Wyo., Verde PR &amp; Consulting is a full-service traditional and digital public relations, marketing, branding, and consulting agency, with an emphasis in sustainability. Verde’s clients are rooted in the outdoor, bike, and snowsports industries, as well as the health and wellness and Lifestyles of Health and Sustainability (LOHAS) markets. For more, visit: <a href=\"http://www.verdepr.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.verdepr.com</a>.\r\n\r\n<strong>About Northside</strong>\r\nNorthside by Triple T Trading is a quality footwear brand for all-seasons, available in contemporary styles. Offering a range of styles from winter boots and trail shoes to sandals and flip-flops, Northside shoes are rugged, reliable and affordable for families who want to enjoy the outdoors together. Triple T Trading, the parent company for the Northside brand was founded in 1985 with the goal to design, manufacture and sell well-made affordable footwear. Northside by Triple T Trading is headquartered in Marysville, Wash. For more information, please visit <a href=\"http://www.northsideusa.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.northsideusa.com</a>.','Northside brings fun outdoor footwear for the whole family  to Outdoor Retailer Summer Market 2012 ','Northside will be introducing new styles for the whole family at Outdoor Retailer Summer Market 2012, Booth #29131','publish','closed','closed','','northside-brings-fun-outdoor-footwear-for-the-whole-family-to-outdoor-retailer-summer-market-2012-2','','','2014-09-15 15:57:38','2014-09-15 15:57:38','',0,'http://northsideusa.com/northside-brings-fun-outdoor-footwear-for-the-whole-family-to-outdoor-retailer-summer-market-2012-2/',0,'post','',0),(18,1,'2013-10-14 19:49:40','2013-10-14 19:49:40','As an independent, family owned and operated business, it’s important to us that our customers feel like an extension of our Northside brand family. Everyone at Northside is dedicated to providing unrivaled service.\r\n\r\n<em>We work hard to build comfortable, functional and durable outdoor footwear. We want you to be 100% satisfied with your purchase.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>If you’re not happy, we’re not happy! </em>\r\n\r\n<em>In the unlikely event that you have an issue with any of our products, contact us at </em><a href=\"mailto:Contactus@Northsideusa.com\">Contact@Northsideusa.com</a><em>.</em>\r\n\r\n<em>\r\n</em>','Brand Promise','',