cf-field&p=21402',0,'acf-field','',0),(21403,1,'2014-11-06 14:42:04','2014-11-06 14:42:04','a:8:{s:4:\"type\";s:5:\"image\";s:12:\"instructions\";s:0:\"\";s:8:\"required\";i:0;s:17:\"conditional_logic\";i:0;s:12:\"column_width\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"preview_size\";s:9:\"thumbnail\";s:7:\"library\";s:3:\"all\";s:13:\"return_format\";s:5:\"array\";}','Icon','icon','publish','open','open','','field_526938a310974','','','2014-11-06 14:42:04','2014-11-06 14:42:04','',21401,'http://northsideusa.com/?post_type=acf-field&p=21403',1,'acf-field','',0),(21355,0,'2012-06-27 12:29:46','1970-01-01 00:00:00','Northside footwear is made for real family&rsquo;s outdoor adventures. Northside features footwear for the entire family that is perfect for casual hiking, camping, and water vacations. The classic designs offer functionality at affordable prices and keep growing kids and the high costs of buying gear in mind. Here are some shoes that you should consider for coverage this summer:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Burke II</strong><br />\r\nPossibly the most popular shoe in the Northside Sport Line, the Burke II is the refined version of it&rsquo;s predecessor. Developed with a contour cushioned brushed EVA insole and TPR outsole for sure-step and foot protection. This amphibious shoe features waterproof PU and EVA lined upper for extra comfort and the Elastic Drawstring Lacing System and Lace Keeper. Available for the whole family is sizes <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Mens-Burke-Sandal-Brown/dp/B005HO2DMC/ref=sr_1_12?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340828783&amp;sr=8-12&amp;keywords=Northside+mens+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">M 8 &ndash; 13</a>, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Womens-Northside-Burke-Hiking-Sandals/dp/B007KTCMOQ/ref=sr_1_2?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340828677&amp;sr=8-2&amp;keywords=Northside+womens+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">W 6-10</a>, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Burke-II-Ankle-Strap-Toddler/dp/B005HNPAV4/ref=sr_1_7?s=shoes&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340828891&amp;sr=1-7&amp;keywords=Northside+toddlers+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">Kids 13-6</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Closed-Sandal-Little-Orange/dp/B004JN0TMI/ref=sr_1_13?s=shoes&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340829692&amp;sr=1-13&amp;keywords=northside+toddler+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">Toddlers 7-12</a>. Men and Women&#039;s SRP $45.00. Kid&#039;s and Toddler SRP $24.95.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Brille II</strong><br />\r\nFrom backyard splashing to camping by the lake, The Northside Brill water shoe provides a comfy combo of neoprene, mesh and nylon with an injected TPR outsole to protect feet and provide traction in and out of the water. Its elastic Drawstring Lacing System and Lace Keeper allow for customizable tightening for a perfect fit. Available for the whole family in sizes <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Brille-Water-Shoe-Mens/dp/B007KTGRR4/ref=sr_1_7?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340828749&amp;sr=8-7&amp;keywords=Northside+mens+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">M 8 &ndash; 13</a>, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Brille-Water-Shoe-Womens/dp/B007KTD47K/ref=sr_1_16?s=shoes&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340829878&amp;sr=1-16&amp;keywords=northside+women+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">W 6 &ndash; 10</a>, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Brille-Water-Shoe-Kids/dp/B004R8G212/ref=sr_1_3?s=shoes&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340828856&amp;sr=1-3&amp;keywords=Northside+kids+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">Kids 13 &ndash; 6</a>, and <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Brille-Water-Shoe-Kids/dp/B007LBU5K6/ref=sr_1_9?s=shoes&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340829692&amp;sr=1-9&amp;keywords=northside+toddler+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">Toddlers 5-12.</a> Men and Women&#039;s <strong>SRP $19.95</strong>. Kid&#039;s and Toddler <strong>SRP $14.95</strong>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Womens-Pioneer-Waterproof-Hiking/dp/B005HMTQH4/ref=sr_1_6?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1341241870&amp;sr=8-6&amp;keywords=northside+womens+shoes\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Women&rsquo;s Pioneer</strong></a><br />\r\nThis mid-cut hiking shoe offers great support for trails, while being comfortable for the campsite. The upper part of the hiker is made from suede and nylon with embosed PVC mudguard, and the Pioneer has a TPR Traction sole. This shoe is great for hiking with the family and relaxing at the campsite. Sizes W 6-10. <strong>SRP</strong> <strong>$44.95</strong>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Ridgecrest-Waterproof-Hiking-Brown/dp/B004OC027Q/ref=sr_1_15?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340828783&amp;sr=8-15&amp;keywords=Northside+mens+shoes\" target=\"_blank\">Men&rsquo;s Ridgecrest Mid</a></strong><br />\r\nThe Ridgecrest is a waterproof mid top that provides durable support on the trail with TPR Traction outsole and an embossed PVC Mudguard. This shoe features a multifunctional, breathable, and washable with Poron insole and lightweight compression molded EVA midsole. Sizes M 8-13. <strong>SRP $59.95</strong>.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Scout-Hiking-Toddler-Little/dp/B004QL9NHA/ref=sr_1_9?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1340829655&amp;sr=8-9&amp;keywords=northside+kids+shoes\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Kid&rsquo;s Scout</strong></a><br />\r\nBoys and girls alike will love the Scout! With a Loop Speed Lacing System, the shoes are easy to slip on and off. The cushioned insole and TPR Traction outsole allows kids to hike, run, and play with comfort and ease. Available in boys&rsquo; sizes (Brown/Orange) 4-7, girls sizes (Tan/Berry) 11-5, and kids sizes (Brown/Orange) 11-3. SRP <strong>$29.95</strong>.','NORTHSIDE Summer Footwear for the Entire Family','Northside introduces summer footwear for the entire family. Get ready for outdoor adventures!','publish','closed','closed','','northside-summer-footwear-for-the-entire-family-2','','','2012-06-27 12:29:46','1970-01-01 00:00:00','',0,'http://northsideusa.com/northside-summer-footwear-for-the-entire-family-2/',0,'post','',0),(21356,0,'2012-05-17 12:01:46','1970-01-01 00:00:00','MARYSVILLE, Wash. (May 17, 2012) &ndash;Northside, a leader in comfortable, durable and affordable outdoor and lifestyle footwear, today announces the selection of Verde PR &amp; Consulting as its agency of record. The partnership will bring additional exposure to Northside within the outdoor and active-lifestyle arenas for their four footwear categories: Trail, Sport, Polar and Lifestyle.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;We are really looking forward to working with Verde PR as we head into Outdoor Retailer Summer Market,&rdquo; said Jack Wolfin, president of Triple T Trading. &ldquo;Their depth of experience in outdoor and lifestyle industries is exactly what we were looking for in a PR partner.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe Northside brand, now 12 years old, represents quality, rugged, reliable and affordable footwear available in contemporary styles for all members of the family. Northside&rsquo;s lighthearted, down to earth branding stems from the company&rsquo;s core values, one of which identifies the importance of lasting experiences that result from families enjoying the outdoors together. The company realizes that people who wear Northside shoes are looking for a reliable, affordable footwear option for outdoor fun.&nbsp;<br />\r\n<br />\r\n&ldquo;A lot of us struggle with that balance of getting outside with our families to do the things we love, without breaking the bank on clothing and footwear,&rdquo; said Kristin Carpenter-Ogden, founder and president of Verde PR. &ldquo;We&rsquo;re excited to be working with a company like Northside that offers great outdoor footwear that parents and families can stand behind.&rdquo;<br />\r\n<br />\r\nVerde PR was founded in the active lifestyle, outdoors, travel, and sustainable-products markets and celebrates its 10-year anniversary this year. Verde PR offices are located in the mountain sport hotbeds of Durango, Boulder, Colo., and Jackson, Wyo.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNorthside shoes are available at more than 500 retailers and major online stores nationwide including Sportsmans Warehouse, Fred Meyer, Super Shoes, Scheels, Amazon.com and others. Northside shoes typically retail from $29 to $69.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n###<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>About Verde PR &amp; Consulting</strong><br />\r\nWith offices in Durango and Boulder, Colo. and Jackson, Wyo., Verde PR &amp; Consulting is a full-service traditional and digital public relations, marketing, branding, and consulting agency, with an emphasis in sustainability. Verde&rsquo;s clients are rooted in the outdoor, bike, and snowsports industries, as well as the health and wellness and Lifestyles of Health and Sustainability (LOHAS) markets. For more, visit: http://www.verdepr.com.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>About Northside</strong><br />\r\nNorthside by Triple T Trading is a quality footwear brand for all-seasons, available in contemporary styles. Offering a range of styles from winter boots and trail shoes to sandals and flip-flops, Northside shoes are rugged, reliable and affordable for families who want to enjoy the outdoors together. Triple T Trading, the parent company for the Northside brand was founded in 1985 with the goal to design, manufacture and sell well-made affordable footwear. Northside by Triple T Trading is headquartered in Marysville, Wash. For more information, please visit www.northsideusa.com.','Northside announces partnership with Verde PR &amp; Consulting','Northside announces partnership with @verdepr','publish','closed','closed','','northside-announces-partnership-with-verde-pr-consulting-2','','','2012-05-17 12:01:46','1970-01-01 00:00:00','',0,'http://northsideusa.com/northside-announces-partnership-with-verde-pr-consulting-2/',0,'post','',0),(21372,1,'2014-09-15 15:55:11','2014-09-15 15:55:11','<!--  /* Font Definitions */ @font-face 	{font-family:Cambria; 	panose-1:2 4 5 3 5 4 6 3 2 4; 	mso-font-charset:0; 	mso-generic-font-family:auto; 	mso-font-pitch:variable; 	mso-font-signature:3 0 0 0 1 0;