rs in inner city Seattle and bring people together. In doing so, Northside made the holidays a little bit warmer for members of a local Boys and Girls Club.\r\n\r\nIn partnership with <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Project Sole\" href=\"projectsole.org\" target=\"_blank\">Project Sole</a></span>, Northside packed up over 500 pairs of shoes and brought them to the <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Smilow Rainier Vista Club\" href=\"http://positiveplace.org/locations/rainiervista/Pages/home.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Joel E. Smilow Clubhouse and Teen Center at Rainier Vista</a></span>. There, children of all ages were fitted with brand new footwear–for free. From pink <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Northside Sneakers\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Girls-Youth-Tempo-Shoes/dp/B00CBNQ1IY/ref=sr_1_55?s=apparel&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1420838366&amp;sr=1-55\" target=\"_blank\">sneakers</a> </span>to waterproof <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Frosty Snow Boots\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Frosty-Winter-Toddler-Little/dp/B00HZ0FOPO/ref=sr_1_1?s=apparel&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1420839610&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=frosty+snow+boot\" target=\"_blank\">snow boots</a></span>, there was a perfect pair for every child.\r\n\r\nJaron Wilson, founder of Project Sole, shared this about being a Sneaker Santa, \"The old adage of: \'Tis better to give than to receive\' rings true at such events like this. The warm smiles, hugs and high-fives from all of the kids makes all of this worth it.\"\r\n\r\nWatch the video and see for yourself the difference new shoes can make.\r\n\r\n<iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/7ZrEsJQZDr4\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\r\n\r\nFrom the video: “We are so grateful to have Northside and Project Sole come here to our club to visit with us, to see what we do, and then to provide shoes for all of our kids. It’s just wonderful. Thank you.”','Northside and Project Sole Make a Difference for the Boys and Girls Club','','publish','open','open','','northside-project-sole','','','2015-01-13 16:09:27','2015-01-13 23:09:27','',0,'https://northsideusa.com/?p=21620',0,'post','',0),(21621,8,'2015-01-12 13:06:31','2015-01-12 20:06:31','Northside Project Sole Happy Girl','Northside Project Sole Happy Girl','','inherit','open','open','','northsideprojectsolehappygirl','','','2015-01-12 13:06:50','2015-01-12 20:06:50','',21620,'https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NorthsideProjectSoleHappyGirl.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(21798,7,'2015-06-28 14:53:57','2015-06-28 20:53:57','','214789W400-(blue)','','inherit','open','open','','214789w400-blue','','','2015-06-28 14:53:57','2015-06-28 20:53:57','',21273,'https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/214789W400-blue.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21799,0,'2015-06-28 15:04:09','2015-06-28 08:04:09','The Kiva is a great sandal for everyday errands, or that special outdoor adventure.  The rubber outsole has our All Terrain Grip (ATG) system for great stability.  The slide release buckle makes it easy to put on.','Kiva','Stylish sandal for every occasion!!!','publish','open','open','','kiva','','','2016-02-16 09:15:31','2016-02-16 02:15:31','',0,'',0,'shopp_product','',0),(21800,7,'2015-06-28 15:06:23','2015-06-28 21:06:23','','215007W410-(navy)','','inherit','open','open','','215007w410-navy','','','2015-06-28 15:06:23','2015-06-28 21:06:23','',21799,'https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/215007W410-navy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21801,7,'2015-06-28 15:28:24','2015-06-28 21:28:24','','412203W044-(gray-aqua)','','inherit','open','open','','412203w044-gray-aqua','','','2015-06-28 15:28:24','2015-06-28 21:28:24','',0,'https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/412203W044-gray-aqua.jpg',0,'a