 align=\"right\"><b>Media Contact:</b></p>  <p align=\"right\">Lisa Mullen</p>  <p align=\"right\">Verde PR &amp; Consulting</p>  <p align=\"right\"><a href=\"mailto:crabun@verdepr.com\">lisa@verdepr.com</a></p>  <p align=\"right\">970-259-3555 </p>  <p align=\"right\"> </p>  <p><b>MARYSVILLE, Wash.</b> (January 21, 2015)<b> – </b><a href=\"http://www.northside.com\">Northside</a>, a leader in footwear for the recreational outdoor enthusiast, unveils an expanded trail line for Fall and Winter 2015/2016 to meet the needs of more consumers than ever before. With an increasing number of adventurers hitting the trails every year, Northside is building on its product offerings to best serve its growing customer base. New boots include added men’s models, updated women’s styles, and a continued focus on hunting offerings.</p>  <p> </p>  <p><i>Highlights for Fall and Winter 2015/2016:</i></p>  <p><b>Men’s Talus Mid WP</b></p>  <p>The Talus is a durable, all-leather waterproof hiker designed for rugged adventures. It offers the comfort of a breathable boot with a contour cushioned insole and padded collar for longer hikes. Extra stability comes from a steel shank and all-terrain outsole to provide grip and traction when traversing tricky surfaces. <b>MSRP $79.99</b> </p>  <p></p>  <p><b>Men’s Atlas Mid WP</b></p>  <p>Built to thrive on burly hikes or for everyday wear, the Atlas is constructed with distressed leather and nylon mesh for ultimate performance and wearability. A waterproof construction keeps you dry, the Northside all-terrain outsole keeps you on your feet, and the aesthetic accents earns style points in any situation. <b>MSRP $69.99</b></p>  <p><b>Women’s Apex Lite WP</b></p>  <p>This women’s version of the best-selling men’s all-leather boot puts a feminine twist on a rugged hiker. The Apex Lite is redesigned for a female-friendly fit without compromising performance. A dual-density lightweight EVA mid-sole, traction outsole and contour-cushioned insole provide comfort while the latest in waterproof booty construction keeps feet dry and warm. <b>MSRP $69.99</b></p>  <p><b>Men’s Banshee</b></p>  <p>The waterproof Banshee is a lightweight all-weather hunting boot that offers warmth and comfort with more than 600g Thermolite insulation, removable contour-cushioned insole, and a durable suede/nylon upper. This unique boot has a heavy-duty PU-embossed shell that provides unmatched protection and added stability with a 9.5” shaft and padded collar. <b>MSRP $89.99</b></p>  <p>For more information on Northside shoes, visit <a href=\"http://www.northsideusa.com\">www.northsideusa.com</a>, and to join our community, visit our <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Northside-USA/151316914912827\">Facebook page</a>. To check out these shoes in person, stop by the Northside booth (#<a href=\"http://n2b.goexposoftware.com/events/ors2014/goExpo/floorPlan/viewFloorPlan.php?ei=496&amp;zb=30137W\">30165W</a>) at Outdoor Retailer, January 21-24, 2015.</p>  <p><b>About Northside</b></p>  <p>Northside by Triple T Trading is a quality footwear brand for all-seasons, available in contemporary styles. Offering a range of styles from winter boots and trail shoes to sandals and flip-flops, Northside shoes are rugged, reliable and affordable for families who want to enjoy the outdoors together. Triple T Trading, the parent company for the Northside brand was founded in 1985 with the goal to design, manufacture and sell well-made affordable footwear. Northside by Triple T Trading is headquartered in Marysville, Wash. For more information, please visit www.northsideusa.com.</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p>  ','Northside Expands Trail Line to Meet More Needs Than Ever Before','','publish','closed','closed','','northside-expands-trail-line-to-meet-more-needs-than-ever-before-6','','','2015-01-12 21:59:59','2015-01-13 04:59:59','',0,'https://northsideusa.com/northside-expands-trail-line-to-meet-more-needs-than-ever-before-6/',0,'post','',0),(21628,8,'2015-01-13 16:08:36','2015-01-13 23:08:36','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-21621\" src=\"https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/NorthsideProjectSoleHappyGirl.png\" alt=\"Northside Project Sole Happy Girl\" width=\"800\" height=\"507\" />\n\nThe holidays are all about bringing people together, whether it’s family around a dinner table or spending time with friends over a cup of hot chocolate. As an independent, family owned and operated business, Northside knows exactly how important it is to bring people together to support and celebrate one another.\n\nThis holiday season, Northside reached out to how they could help their neighbors in inner city Seattle and bring people together. In doing so, Northside made the holidays a little bit warmer for members of a local Boys and Girls Club.\n\nIn partnership with <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Project Sole\" href=\"projectsole.org\" target=\"_blank\">Project Sole</a></span>, Northside packed up over 500 pairs of shoes and brought them to the <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Smilow Rainier Vista Club\" href=\"http://positiveplace.org/locations/rainiervista/Pages/home.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">Joel E. Smilow Clubhouse and Teen Center at Rainier Vista</a></span>. There, children of all ages were fitted with brand new footwear–for free. From pink <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Northside Sneakers\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Girls-Youth-Tempo-Shoes/dp/B00CBNQ1IY/ref=sr_1_55?s=apparel&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1420838366&amp;sr=1-55\" target=\"_blank\">sneakers</a> </span>to waterproof <span style=\"color: #ff6600;\"><a style=\"color: #ff6600;\" title=\"Frosty Snow Boots\" href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Northside-Frosty-Winter-Toddler-Little/dp/B00HZ0FOPO/ref=sr_1_1?s=apparel&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1420839610&amp;sr=1-1&amp;keywords=frosty+snow+boot\" target=\"_blank\">snow boots</a></span>, there was a perfect pair for every child.\n\nJaron Wilson, founder of Project Sole, shared this from the \"The old adage of: \'Tis better to give than to receive\' rings true at such events like this. The warm smiles, hugs and high-fives from all of the kids makes all of this worth it.\"\n\nWatch the video and see for yourself the difference new shoes can make.\n\n<iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/7ZrEsJQZDr4\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe>\n\nFrom the video: “We are so grateful to have Northside and Project Sole come here to our club to visit with us, to see what we do, and then to provide shoes for all of our kids. It’s just wonderful. Thank you.”','Northside and Project Sole Make a Difference for the Boys and Girls Club','','inherit','open','open','','21620-autosave-v1','','','2015-01-13 16:08:36','2015-01-13 23:08:36','',21620,'https://northsideusa.com/21620-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(21712,7,'2015-03-05 15:44:01','2015-03-05 22:44:01','','314993k905_001-copy','','inherit','open','open','','314993k905_001-copy','','','2015-03-05 15:44:01','2015-03-05 22:44:01','',21710,'https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/314993k905_001-copy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21713,7,'2015-03-05 15:44:04','2015-03-05 22:44:04','','314993k905_002-copy','','inherit','open','open','','314993k905_002-copy','','','2015-03-05 15:44:04','2015-03-05 22:44:04','',21710,'https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/314993k905_002-copy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21714,7,'2015-03-05 15:44:06','2015-03-05 22:44:06','','314993k905_003-copy','','inherit','open','open','','314993k905_003-copy','','','2015-03-05 15:44:06','2015-03-05 22:44:06','',21710,'https://northsideusa.com/2014/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/314993k905_003-copy.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(21715,7,'2015-03-05 15:44:08','2015-03-05 22:44:08','','314993k905_004-copy','','inherit','open','open','','314993k905_004-c