INSERT INTO `products` VALUES (1,'Abilene 400',NULL,'The Abilene Hunting Boot keeps feet fully protected and toasty warm while outside in the field. The suede and camo nylon upper is fully seam-sealed and topped with a waterproof membrane, ensuring that feet stay dry. The boot is packed with a 400 grams of Thermolite insulation, rated at -40°F, for unbelievable warmth. The washable insole offers excellent support and breathability, while the embossed leather mud guard and heel stabilizer yield superior traction against trail obstacles. The lightweight, compression-molded EVA midsole provides ample cushioning where you need it most. The tough rubber outsole delivers superior traction on a variety of rugged terrains. Lace-up design.',0.00,79.99,'f','a',NULL,21214,1,'2016-06-13 17:18:39','2016-06-13 17:18:39'),(2,'Brille II','Great water shoe for those wetter adventures!','The Brille II water shoe is great choice for almost any adventure.  Great for those walks along the beach, or stepping on rocks in your favorite stream.  The flexible TPR sole provides great wet or dry traction.  The breathable neoprene mesh upper allows for quick drying.',0.00,19.99,'f','a',NULL,21802,1,'2016-06-13 17:18:39','2016-06-13 17:18:39'),(3,'Burke II','Go anywhere, do anything footwear!!!','The Burke II is a outstanding choice for a walk in the park, a stroll down the beach, or running errands downtown. The open design allows for cool ventilation and drainage for those wet beach times. Easy to slip into with the quick cord lacing system.',0.00,29.99,'f','a',NULL,21761,1,'2016-06-13 17:18:39','2016-06-13 17:18:39'),(4,'Apex Mid','An excellent choice for day long hikes!','The sturdy Apex Mid is constructed of a distressed leather upper and a padded collar and tongue to keep you comfortable on the trail for day hikes or multi-day adventures.  A compression-molded insole adds to the comfort and support.  With full waterproof booty construction, the Apex Mid is bolstered with a reinforced toe box for added protection from rocks and roots, along with Northside’s All Terrain Grip Outsole with trail-specific lug patterns for exceptional grip and control on varied terrain.',0.00,69.99,'m','a',NULL,59,1,'2016-06-28 18:05:12','2016-06-28 18:05:12'),(5,'Blackstone','A rugged cold weather boot to keep you warm and dry!','The full-featured 8” Blackstone boot sports a heavy duty upper constructed of leather and nylon with a D-ring speed lacing system for maximum fit.  This boot is built for snow with 200 grams of Thermolite insulation and full boot, seam sealed, waterproof construction.  A padded collar, removable berber lined insole and TPR shell ensure your feet stay warm, dry and comfortable through those long winter days and nights.',0.00,64.99,'m','a',NULL,21861,1,'2016-06-28 18:08:51','2016-06-28 18:08:51'),(6,'Burke II','On the go footwear, for the on the go lifestyle!','The Burke II is a outstanding choice for a walk in the park, a stroll down the beach, or running errands downtown. The open design allows for cool ventilation and drainage for those wet beach times. Easy to slip into with the quick cord lacing system.',0.00,29.99,'m','a',NULL,21774,1,'2016-06-28 18:08:51','2016-06-28 18:08:51'),(7,'Back Country','Designed to take on the cold, wet winter!','Based on the men\'s Back Country, the kids Back Country Jr. has all the features and functions of Dad\'s boot.  Removable insulated felt liner with berber collar makes this boot fit like a glove.  The TPR waterproof shell combined with the waterproofed micro suede upper will insure your kids feet stay warm and dry during the longest snow ball fights and deepest snow.',0.00,54.99,'u','k',NULL,21160,1,'2016-06-28 18:27:59','2016-06-28 18:27:59'),(8,'Brille II','Designed to take on the cold, wet winter!','The Brille II water shoe is perfect for the kid who likes water fun.  The flexible sole provides great traction on those slippery stones along the shore line or in the nearby creek.  The neoprene mesh upper is breathable and allows for quick drying.  This water shoe is the go anywhere shoe for those adventures involving water!',0.00,16.99,'u','k',NULL,21806,1,'2016-06-28 18:27:59','2016-06-28 18:27:59'),(9,'Burke II','Active footwear for the active kid!!!','The Burke II is a outstanding choice for running through the park, splashing in the water, or just about any everyday adventure. The open design allows for cool ventilation and drainage for when water is unavoidable. Easy to slip into with the quick cord lacing system.',0.00,26.99,'u','k',NULL,21966,1,'2016-06-28 18:27:59','2016-06-28 18:27:59'),(10,'Acadia II','','The Acadia II is the perfect pull-on, do-anything winter boot. With a front zip for easy on and off, warm Thermolite insulation, a waterproof TPR shell, and a removable EVA insole with a stylish faux-fur collar, this boot is cold weather go-to all season long.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,177,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(11,'Akira II','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21286,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(12,'Alma','','The Cabrillo II is the ultimate lounge-ready slipper. With a cushy synthetic suede upper, a warm and cozy micro-chenille lining, and a cute contrast stitching design, the Cabrillo II is your best friend for a family movie day.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,90,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(13,'Apex Lite WP','','This women’s version of the best-selling men’s Apex all-leather hiker puts a feminine twist on a rugged performance boot.  Trimmed down on a sleek dual density EVA compression molded mid-sole for comfort and performance.  To ensure your feet stay dry and comfortable this boot incorporates the latest in waterproof boot construction with the Northside EVA contour cushioned removable insole.  This boot will fit like a glove while providing high level of performance during short or extended outdoor activities.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21854,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(14,'Back Country','','This snowboot offers full protection from the elements with a waterproof suede/nubuck upper, 200g of Thermolite insulation, and grippy, cleated rubber sole. Sturdy and protective, and designed to keep your feet warm and dry no matter the weather, the Back Country is the workhorse of your winter wardrobe.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,15566,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(15,'Becka','','The sporty Becka winter boot has a bit of Euro flair to help you stand out in any cold-weather setting. The 13-inch rip-stop nylon uppers in bright colors are splayed with horizontal piping that matches the contrasted laces. Foam insulation keeps feet warm and toasty down to -10 degrees F, and All Terrain Grip lugged outsoles help grip on snow and ice. These boots snug up easily with a nylon loop speed lacing system.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,82,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(16,'Bishop','','Wrap your feet in warm cold weather style with the Bishop! These all weather boots feature Nordic knit fabric accenting, faux fur trim, and Nor-Foam insulation rated to -10°F. Stay trendy and toasty warm all winter in the Bishop!',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,80,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(17,'Brille II','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21296,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(18,'Cabrillo II','','The Cabrillo II is the ultimate lounge-ready mule slipper. With a cushy synthetic suede upper, a warm and cozy micro-chenille lining, and a cute contrast stitching design, the Cabrillo II is your best friend for a family movie day.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,89,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(19,'Cali','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,79,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(20,'Carolina','','With a sleeping bag look and feel and hardy TPR outsole, the Carolina slipper booties are just calling to be worn while on a camping trip when you’re sitting around a campfire. They’re also a great option for around the house. The upper is an insulated quilted nylon and synthetic suede that is fleece lined. A fleece-covered, foam-cushioned insole adds to warmth and comfort. Comes in three colors.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,87,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(21,'Cascadia','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21271,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(22,'Catalina','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21300,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(23,'Copeland','','This low-profile hiker emphasizes breathability, comfort and support on the trail and is designed just for women. The mesh and suede upper is embossed with PVC to resist abrasion and comes in three color-ways for a bright, feminine touch. The PVC mudguard and molded pieces on the ankle bolster protection and support. The outsole is lugged for varied trail conditions with All Terrain Grip, and a compression-molded EVA midsole helps to soak up shock. Adjusting the laces is easy with a nylon loop speed lacing system.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,15560,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(24,'Corona','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21277,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(25,'Cypress','','The cute, on-trend Cypress slippers will have your feet looking so good, you’ll want to show them off. With a cushy synthetic suede upper, the real charm kicks in with a plush fold-over tongue, topped with a grosgrain ribbon. The plush-covered foam cushioned insole offers ultimate comfort, and the TPR indoor/outoor sole means these can take you for a quick grocery run and back.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,91,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(26,'Fairmont','','With a stylish micro-chenille faux fur collar and functional waterproof, insulated construction, these will be the envy of women everywhere you go. Thermolite keeps feet warm to -25 degrees F. Waterproof rubber outsoles serve up even more protection from the elements, with sturdy All Terrain lugs for great traction on snow and ice. The Fairmont snugs easily with nylon loop speed lacing system.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,15580,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(27,'Freemont','','Quicken your step with the mid-profile, lightweight Freemont. Crafted from a brightly-accented suede and mesh upper and a lightweight compression-molded EVA midsole, this versatile waterproof boot thrives in all types of terrain. Great for multi-day hikes.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,15585,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(28,'Freemont','','The Freemont hiker is a great combination of outdoor styling, comfort and performance. This mid-cut hiker is fully seam sealed with a booty construction to insure your feet stay dry on the wettest of hikes. The mesh and suede leather constructed upper provides support and protection when on the trail. The removable and washable contour cushioned EVA insole creates a comfortable footbed for all day wear.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21265,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(29,'Kamilla','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,84,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(30,'Katmandu','','The Kathmandu winter boot surrounds your foot with 200 grams of Thinsulate insulation keeping you warm on the coldest of winter days.  The 12.5\" upper is weather ready and waterproof, with a faux-fur touch for extra style points.  The all-rubber outsole serves up even greater protection along with a D-ring lacing system for an easy-on fit.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21876,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(31,'Kayla','','Cure for the common cold! Keep tootsies toasty with these insulated -10°F rated Kayla Sport Mocs. They look sharp, feel good and sport flexibility for natural stride.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,78,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(32,'Kiona LTC','','The Kiona LTC is a women’s-specific light hiking or walking shoe that features an ultra-lightweight soft shell breathable mesh for a comfortable fit, a mudguard for extra protection, and a heel stabilizer for added security on the move. The high traction outsole allows easy transition from road to trail.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,76,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(33,'Kiva','Stylish sandal for every occasion!!!','The Kiva is a great sandal for everyday errands, or that special outdoor adventure.  The rubber outsole has our All Terrain Grip (ATG) system for great stability.  The slide release buckle makes it easy to put on.',0.00,34.99,'f','a',NULL,21799,1,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(34,'Laurel','','With a sleeping bag look and feel and hardy TPR outsole, the Laurel mule-style slippers are just calling to be worn around the house or around a campfire. The upper is an insulated quilted nylon and synthetic suede that is fleece lined. A fleece-covered, foam-cushioned insole adds to warmth and comfort.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,88,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(35,'Madison','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21298,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(36,'Monroe Low','Comfortable footwear for every day use!','This low cut version of our best selling Monroe provides all of the same features as our mid-cut boot including a breathable nylon mesh construction on a solid TPR outsole.  Daily comfort at a great price.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21668,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(37,'Mont Blanc','Warm comfort for those cold winter days!!!','The 9.5\" Mont Blanc is a great combination of style, fashion and performance.  With 200 grams of Thinsulate insulation and waterproof leather, this boot will keep you warm and dry throughout the coldest of winter days.   The padded faux fur collar and soft inner lining make this boot perfect for every day and every night fun.',0.00,89.99,'f','a',NULL,21882,1,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(38,'Pioneer','Lightweight support for the casual hiker!','This supportive boot makes hitting the trail easy. Ideal for the first time and casual hikers, the Pioneers lightweight comfortable fit lets you blaze your own trail.',0.00,39.99,'f','a',NULL,21268,1,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(39,'Redondo','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21303,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(40,'Saint Helens','','Get everyone geared up with these toasty-warm Boots . You\'ll appreciate the warmth from the 200 gram insulation, as well as the peace of mind knowing your kids aren\'t suffering from frozen feet while out playing in the snow. These also provide top traction over ice and snow!',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,178,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(41,'Sitka','','The slip-on Sitka is the perfect go-to footwear when the snow starts to fly. The suede upper is styled with nylon accent stitch and lined with oh-so-cozy poly blend shearling. Added comfort comes from the poly blend shearling-covered EVA insoles that contour to your feet the more you wear them. With durable TPR rubber outsoles, the Sitka can be worn indoors and out.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,83,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(42,'Slater','','The Slater winter boot grants cold-weather protection with flair, with 11-inch herringbone patterned uppers and a padded faux fur collar that can hold their own in any winter-weather situation. Foam insulation keeps feet warm and toasty down to -10 degrees F. All Terrain Grip outsoles are lugged for traction on snow and ice.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,81,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(43,'Snohomish','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21884,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(44,'Snohomish Low','Great looking footwear for the active lifestyle!','The versatile Snohomish is the go-to hiking boot for any adventure. The suede/mesh, waterproof upper means that you can just as easily trek through the summer heat as slosh through spring downpours and stay cool, dry, and comfortable. A TPR sole and mudguard adds additional protection from roots and rocks on the trail, and a Northside contour cushioned insole will keep your feet happy, even on longer outings.',0.00,49.99,'f','a',NULL,21666,1,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(45,'Sun Peak','Comfort, warmth, and style for those winter outings!','Face the winter in style with the Sun Peak women’s full function winter boot.  The Sun Peak is 12.5” all suede leather fashion boot with a stylish knit collar.   Fully seamed sealed this boot provides protection from the elements while looking good.  Clean, classic styling on an all-rubber all-weather shell bottom with 200 grams of Thinsulate insulation make the Sun Peaks a classic winter boot for all occasions and activities.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21910,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(46,'Sun Ridge','','Looking for something easy, the Sun Ridge is the latest Northside front zip boot for winter weather.  All suede with classic stitching detail and a plush faux fur collar make for a great looking combination of style and comfort. An EVA liner with 200g Thermolite insulation and a waterproof TPR outsole provide top tier protection and warmth.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21852,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(47,'Sydney','','With a distressed micro-suede upper and padded plush collar and lining, the cozy Sydney looks more like a winter boot than a slipper. Fold them down or wear them up, it’s your style choice for the look and feel you want. With sturdy TPR outsole, the Sydney can be worn both indoors or out and feels just as at home with your favorite pair of jeans as with your sweatpants. Comes in three colors.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,86,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(48,'Tori','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,15656,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(49,'Trinidad','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21758,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(50,'Trinidad','Go anywhere open footwear!!!','The stylish Trindad is great for that walk in the park, or running errands around time. The upper is constructed with leather and neoprene. It has an easy to use drawstring lacing system and an adjustable hook &amp; loop heel strap.',0.00,54.99,'f','a',NULL,21273,1,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(51,'Trinity','','',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21289,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(52,'Winthrop II','','This 9\" all suede boot, has a great combination of outdoor styling with a padded berber collar, lacing accents and nylon loop speed lacing system for ease of use. The waterproof lightweight TPR shell and 200 grams of Thermolite insulation make the Winthrop II a serious winter weather boot. This a perfect boot for those cold snowy days outside with your friends or family.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,21573,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(53,'Yucatan','','Lined with cozy Berber fleece, the easy-to-slip-on Yucatan will keep your feet cozy indoors and out. Added comfort comes from the Berber -covered EVA insoles that contour to your feet the more you wear them. With durable TPR rubber outsoles, the Yucatan can easily be worn around the house or down to the mailbox. Choose from three colors.',0.00,NULL,'f','a',NULL,85,0,'2016-07-05 13:58:21','2016-07-05 13:58:21'),(73,'Alberta II','','The Alberta II Waterproof Pac Boot delivers maximum warmth and comfort on cold-weather days and nights. The durable nylon upper cinches up easily with a hook-and-loop strap and toggle collar to ensure a customized fit. The removable polypropylene liner with foil bottom is packed with 200 grams of Thermolite insulation to keep feet cozy and warm. The lightweight, waterproof TPR outsole has a trail-specific lug pattern for superior traction, durability, and flexible on all kinds of terrain. The Alberta II Pac Boot is comfort rated at -40°F. 13\" shaft height',0.00,59.99,'m','a',NULL,21535,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(74,'Atlas Mid WP','','The sturdy Apex Mid is constructed of a distressed leather upper and a padded collar and tongue to keep you comfortable on the trail for day hikes or multi-day adventures. A compression-molded insole adds to the comfort and support. With full waterproof boot construction, the Apex Mid is bolstered with a reinforced toe box for added protection from rocks and roots, along with Northside’s All Terrain Grip Outsole with trail-specific lug patterns for exceptional grip and control on varied terrain.',0.00,69.99,'m','a',NULL,21856,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(75,'Back Country','Take on the cold, wet winter with the Back Country!','The classic Back Country is a cornerstone of the Northside Polar line.  11\" suede and nubuck leather combined with a fully removable 8mm felt liner make this boot both stylish and warm.  With sealed seams and a topical DWR coating this boot will keep you warm and dry in the worst winter weather.',0.00,89.99,'m','a',NULL,101,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(76,'Base Camp','','The Base Camp is a rock-solid, rugged hiker for your backpacking adventures. This mountaineering inspired boot is waterproof and breathable with an 8-inch leather and nylon upper to protect from the elements. The lugged All Terrain Grip Outsole serves up great traction and durability for varied trail conditions, with a brushed rubber mudguard on the toe and heel and an abrasion-resistant area on the arch for even more protection. Specially designed paneling on the back of the boot creates a comfortable, flexible fit. Add in a dual-density EVA midsole with a TPU heel cradle for stability, along with easy-grip high tensile laces, and this boot will be your best friend on multi-day trips in the backcountry.',0.00,90.00,'m','a',NULL,52,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(77,'Bismarck','A go anywhere hiker featuring our Daybreak brand camo!','Incorporating the latest Northside Daybreak Camo, the Bismarck is a sturdy suede and nylon hiker.  Built on a rugged TPR outsole with a comfort padded tongue and collar and contoured EVA insole this boot will provide all-day comfort whether hiking, hunting or hanging out.',0.00,54.99,'m','a',NULL,21479,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(78,'Brille II','','',0.00,19.00,'m','a',NULL,21252,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(79,'Coldcreek','','The Coldcreek all-weather boot is constructed of durable neoprene and rubber on a full traction sole. Fully waterproof with the added benefit of insulation and full contour cushioned removable insole make this boot perfect for multi faceted outdoor activities.',0.00,79.99,'m','a',NULL,21491,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(80,'Cornice','A rugged boot for work or play!!!','Look no further for an all distressed leather, insulated, waterproof pac boot. The Cornice has all of the features of a heavy duty outdoor work and snow boot without the price.  This boot incorporates a extra insulated removable felt liner and seam sealed and sprayed waterpoofing for the best in warm, dry comfort.',0.00,79.99,'m','a',NULL,21557,1,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(81,'Dawson','','Work boot, play boot all around town boot. The Dawson is an easy on easy off slip on boot built for the fall and winter weather.  The TPR waterproof shell will get you through the puddles, to the soccer field or out in your yard.  The 200 grams of Thermolite insulation will keep your feet warm as those temperatures drop into full winter mode.',0.00,39.99,'m','a',NULL,168,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(82,'Everest','','The heavy-duty all suede leather Everest is build tough for the deepest and coldest of snow storms. At 10\" tall with a removable insulating liner, this boot is super comfortable and functional. The TPR shell and deep grip sole make for a great combination of warmth, durability and traction during all your snow day activites.',0.00,64.99,'m','a',NULL,163,0,'2016-07-06 13:49:15','2016-07-06 13:49:15'),(83,'Granger II','','The Granger II with 600 gram Thermolite® Insulation locks in heat to keep your feet toasty w